<h1>Aqua Planet Jeju</h1>
<p>We had enough time before our t'way Airlines flight to visit one more attraction. Aqua Planet is a Sea World-like aquarium with marine-themed shows for the kids. Families will enjoy the circus show on water, and have a chance to interact with some fish and marine animals. The giant sting ray is an amazing specimen, with an unusually friendly-looking smile. But perhaps most impressive about Aqua Planet is the location and amazing picturesque view just outside the food court. A great spot to take photos of the ocean and a crater in the background.</p>
